ratings.comment: Kaitlin was a great professor and put a lot of thought into all of her lectures. She would dissect the minutia of a scene and making you look at it differently. She gave honest feedback, great film recommendations, and was very caring to sit down with students to go over their edits.

Professor Fyfe does a really good job of making the topics covered in lecture easy to understand. I enjoyed every lecture and actually looked forward to going. She went the extra mile to make sure that everyone was comprehending the topics covered and was more than happy to answer any questions. I would definitely take another class from her.

I took com arts 350 with Professor Fyfe and I loved it. Her knowledge of film is astonishing. I learned so much from this class. You have to pay attention in discussion and lecture to be able to complete the assignments, but it's not too hard because the lectures are amazing. If you have an interest in film I definitely recommend this class!
